
Interconnected pseudorandom systems

Each layer creates a semantic-noise channel that affects another layer.

Pond theme
  Fish layer
  Lilipad layer
  Particle layer
  Sound wave layer


Brainstorming

Player can drag locations of lilipads

Lilipads cause shadows

Shadows affect algae growth

Algae growth creates food particles

Fish are autonomous agents that move towards nearest food particles.

Fish positions cause waves in the soundwave layer.
